data.description: Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom family home in Lubbock, TX. Boasting a spacious layout, this residence features a comfortable 2-car garage, along with two inviting living areas that provide ample space for relaxation and entertainment. The warm and inviting interior is complemented by an abundance of natural light, while the well-maintained backyard offers a perfect setting for outdoor gatherings. Nestled in a family-friendly neighborhood and conveniently located, this home presents an ideal opportunity for those seeking both comfort and functionality. Schedule your showing today!
